# =============================================================================
# üéØ NODE-SPECIFIC SERVICE MAPPING
# =============================================================================
# This section maps each node type to its required backend services:

# sayNode requires:
# - VITE_TTS_ADAPTER_URL (speech synthesis)
# - VITE_STREAMING_TTS_ADAPTER_URL (real-time speech)

# collectNode requires:
# - VITE_ASR_ADAPTER_URL (speech recognition)
# - VITE_VAD_SERVICE_URL (voice activity detection)

# transferNode requires:
# - VITE_CALL_TRANSFER_URL (call transfer logic)
# - VITE_VOICE_ROUTER_URL (call routing)
# - VITE_TELEPHONY_ADAPTER_URL (telephony integration)

# decisionNode requires:
# - VITE_DECISION_ENGINE_URL (decision logic)
# - VITE_AI_VOICE_INTELLIGENCE_URL (intelligent routing)

# llmNode requires:
# - VITE_DIALOG_ORCHESTRATOR_URL (conversation management)
# - VITE_AI_VOICE_INTELLIGENCE_URL (AI processing)

# hangupNode requires:
# - VITE_TELEPHONY_ADAPTER_URL (call termination)
# - VITE_CALL_RECORDING_URL (call recording if enabled)

# All nodes require:
# - VITE_FLOW_PROCESSOR_URL (execution)
# - VITE_API_GATEWAY_URL (data flow)
# - VITE_FLOW_DESIGNER_URL (management)
